{"prompt": "Create a portal for a community support group. The site's branding should utilize a subtle yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Support Portal</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fefbd8; /* Subtle Yellow Background */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #f9e784; /* Slightly deeper yellow for header */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #e8d85a 3px solid; /* Darker yellow border */\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 36px;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #main-content h2 {\n            color: #e8d85a; /* Yellow for section titles */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .card {\n            background: #fff;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;\n        }\n        .card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n        .card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #f9e784; /* Yellow for card titles */\n        }\n        .button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: #f9e784; /* Yellow button */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .button:hover {\n            background: #e8d85a; /* Darker yellow on hover */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #f9e784; /* Yellow footer */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .contact-info {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .contact-info p {\n            margin: 5px 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Community Support Portal</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div id=\"main-content\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Welcome to Our Support Community</h2>\n        <p>A safe space to connect, share, and find support.</p>\n\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <h3>Upcoming Events</h3>\n            <p>Join us for our weekly online meet-up this Thursday at 7 PM. Share your experiences and hear from others.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"button\">View Calendar</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <h3>Resources</h3>\n            <p>Find helpful articles, guides, and links to external support services.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"button\">Browse Resources</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <h3>Forum</h3>\n            <p>Engage in discussions, ask questions, and offer support to fellow community members.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"button\">Visit Forum</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <h3>Get Involved</h3>\n            <p>Learn how you can contribute to our community and help others.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"button\">Learn More</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"contact-info\">\n            <h3>Contact Us</h3>\n            <p>Email: support@community.example.com</p>\n            <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Community Support. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}